elements.name: Como usuario, intento crear un miembro con datos inválidos y luego corrijo el error para completar la creación

steps.name: I am correctly authenticated with "<USERNAME>" and "<PASSWORD>"
I go to the members page
I want to add a new member
I fill in the member name with "<MEMBER_2_NAME>" and email with "<MEMBER_2_EMAIL_INVALID>"
I press the save button to create the new member
I fill in the member name with "<MEMBER_2_NAME>" and email with "<MEMBER_2_EMAIL>"
I should not see a red border indicating a validation error
The member is successfully created and listed in the members page
